  "texts": [
    "The correlation score is computed for every chosen pair of features.",
    "Blue (-1) indicates a strong negative connection between characteristics, whereas Red (+1) signifies a significant positive association.",
    "The colour white, denoted by the value of 0, signifies the absence of any association between the characteristics.",
    "The feature names are represented in the \"PROGRAM_NAME\"_\"FEATURE_NAME\" format"
  ],
